## Key Features

### Logging

Use the built-in logger instead of console.log:

```typescript
import { logger } from '@/lib/core/logger';

logger.info('User logged in', { userId: user.id });
logger.error('Failed to fetch', { error: err.message });
```

### Configuration

Access environment variables through the config module:

```typescript
import { config, getServerConfig } from '@/lib/core/config';

// Client-safe config
const appName = config.appName;

// Server-only config
const apiKey = getServerConfig().apiKey;
```

